ars all heat if they haven’t moved – including involuntary movement – since the end of their previous turn.</p></details><details><summary>ABLATIVE SHIELDING</summary><p>The Scourer has Resistance to Energy damage.</p></details><details><summary>SUPERCHARGED</summary><p>Characters affected by Focus Down are also Shredded and Slowed until the end of their next turn.</p></details><details><summary>MELT</summary><p>The Scourer makes a ranged attack against an object, deployable or Drone within Range 10, dealing 20 AP Energy damage on a success.</p></details></div>"
